On Kate's laptop:
cd /opt/local/libexec/Geant4/Geant4.10.6/
source geant4.sh
[go back to build dir]
export G4LEDATA="/opt/local/share/Geant4/Data/Geant4.10.6/G4EMLOW7.9"
[above corrects a mistake in the setup script that will cause crashes]
cmake -DGeant4_DIR=/opt/local/lib/Geant4/Geant4.10.6/Geant4-10.6.3 ..

On Cedar:
cmake -DGeant4_DIR= /cvmfs/soft.computecanada.ca/easybuild/software/2020/avx2/Compiler/gcc9/geant4/10.06/lib64/Geant4-10.6.0/ .. 
